		oneko - Neko runs over the windows.
		~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
		A supplement to README for patchlevel 1.2.sakura.5
		~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

				Original program "xneko" written by
							Masayuki Koba
				Modified to program "oneko" by
							Tatsuya Kato
				Modified furthermore by
							John Lerchey
